        <title>[Day 18] 閑著沒事 - NTP 反射攻擊</title>
        <link>https://windasunny.github.io/p/day-18-%E9%96%91%E8%91%97%E6%B2%92%E4%BA%8B-ntp-%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%84%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A/</link>
